OL,3,CD-Day veteran's great grandson born
OL,4,Cduring 80th anniversary commemorations
OL,6,FA 100-year-old war veteran who was the
OL,7,Fyoungest RAF sergeant to land on D-Day
OL,8,Fsaid his great grandson was born as a
OL,9,Fferry took him to Normandy to
OL,10,Fcommemorate the 80th D-Day anniversary.
OL,12,FFormer RAF Sergeant and Royal British
OL,13,FLegion (RBL) ambassador Bernard Morgan
OL,14,Fwas honoured during the D-Day
OL,15,Fcelebrations on Thursday as he was
OL,16,Fpushed in his wheelchair to the
OL,17,Fmarquee by Prime Minister Rishi Sunak.
OL,19,FBut his visit was made extra special
OL,20,Fas he received news of the newest
OL,21,Fmember to his family.
