OL,3,CD-Day veteran's great grandson born
OL,4,Cduring 80th anniversary commemorations
OL,6,FHe met with the King and Queen last
OL,7,Fweek at Buckingham Palace, where he
OL,8,Fand other D-Day veterans shared
OL,9,Fstories and keepsakes, before
OL,10,Fattending the national commemorative
OL,11,Fevent in Ver-sur-Mer on Thursday with
OL,12,FCharles and Camilla.
OL,14,FMr Morgan said he had made the journey
OL,15,Fto pay tribute his fellow soldiers to
OL,16,Fbid them a "final farewell".
