OL,6,FRBL director of Remembrance Philippa
OL,7,FRawlinson said: "It's been an
OL,8,Fincredibly moving and poignant week
OL,9,Ffor the Royal British Legion,
OL,10,Fescorting 21 D-Day veterans and their
OL,11,Fcompanions to Normandy, including the
OL,12,Famazing Bernard."
